# ION Glass & 3D Visual Standards

These rules are auto-generated by ion-dex-commander. Cursor must follow them.

## Trade-Offs
- DO NOT deviate from theme.css color values under any circumstance
- NO gradient-only backgrounds — always include backdrop-blur + rgba

## Visual Metric Constraints
| Property | Value | Tolerance |
|----------|-------|-----------|
| Glass backdrop-blur | ≥ 20px | ±2px |
| Glass background alpha | ≤ 0.40 | ±0.05 |
| Card border glow (cyan) | 0 0 18px rgba(36,247,255,0.35) | ±2px |
| Card border glow (magenta) | 0 0 28px rgba(255,59,212,0.25) | ±2px |
| 3D rotation | ≤ 2° or none | Not to exceed |
| Font: headings | Inter / 900 / tracking-wide | — |
| Font: body | Inter / 400 / tracking-normal | — |
| Neon rim color | #24f7ff (cyan), #ff3bd4 (magenta) | No deviation |

## Anti-Patterns (NEVER DO)
- background-blend-mode: overlay
- background-color alpha > 0.45 inside neon-glass-card__inner
- backdrop-filter: none on glass cards
- rotateX/Y > 5° for static cards
- gradient-only backgrounds without blur
- hardcoded data sources (always use useApiResource or backend API)
